#######
#ingame
#######

^#5aa9d6;Adds glow effect to let you know your hammer or axe is charged and ready to swing.^reset;

Glow begins 0.02 seconds before charge is ready in order to account for reaction time.
Check out Argle Bargles Easier Hammers and Axes or my own Windup Armory Tweaks (Auto) for other swing options.

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

######
#steam
######

[h1]Adds glow effect to let you know your hammer or axe is charged and ready to swing.[/h1]
Glow begins 0.02 seconds before charge is ready in order to account for reaction time.
Check out Argle Bargles [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=787655233] Easier Hammers and Axes[/url] or my own [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=782921923]Windup Armory Tweaks (Auto)[/url] for other swing options.

[url=community.playstarbound.com/threads/124193/]MEGATHREAD[/url]
Find the server version on [url=https://github.com/IsaacHart/sbmod-windarm/releases/tag/0.2]git.[/url]

